Second Department,

May, 1940.

(May 6, 1940.) Rubin Albert and Max Albert, Trading as the Albert Press, Respondents, v. Elizabeth Vilkomerson, Appellant.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Appellate Division denied, without costs. Present — Lazansky, P. J., Hagarty, Carswell, Adel and Taylor, JJ.
